articles.author: Developer DAO (🧱, 🚀)
articles.description:
RT Sam aka ScaryBarbie 👽
i started dabbling in crypto in 2021 when i lost my job as a server.
-started trading
-decided i needed to do something with my time during quarantine & dove into learning how to code
-built a following of 30k on instagram by sharing my learning exp journey daily
-maintained and grew a community
ultimately learning more than just code
-how to market myself
-work w/ brands/collaborations
-design, create content, edit videos
-UX/UI design
-writing/comms
-how to learn quickly & effectively
all these skills were self-taught through learning and failing (repeat x100)
i then made the leap over to twitter & got involved in web3 communities that accelerated my journey by providing opportunities for me to travel & attend hackathons/workshops (big thanks to @womenbuildweb3 @developer_dao & @camiinthisthang)
i wouldn't be where i am if it weren't for being brave enough to take risks even in painful scary times & searching for communities that paved paths for me i didn't even know where possible.
i'm forever grateful to be in this industry surrounded by brilliant people creating & building everyday 🫡
